{"tid":1030463,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"lady gaga取消婚約 傳因未婚夫另有新歡","createTime":"2019-02-21T03:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T08:06:35.000Z","uid":43804,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91d325a72ddb680b02eb79566f91b70ab8767141","tid":1030463,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"開頭仲以為係因為a star is born添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來係個男人有女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>但冇圖</del></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190220/20616306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616306&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e9d9f468\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616306&h=36ed6073\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190220/20616306</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190220/large/20ee2p9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F20ee2p9a.jpg&h=5030c95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天后Lady GaGa的未婚夫Christian Carino，本月8日被目擊手拖一名女伴到荷李活的高級餐廳撐枱腳，與GaGa似乎分手已成定局。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，Christian當日跟深色頭髮索女共晉浪漫晚餐，其間更手拖手，態度親密。事隔兩日，GaGa脫去手上的訂婚戒指出席格林美頒獎禮，情人節更新社交網時也未有提起另一半，是GaGa繼與男星Taylor Kinney取消婚約後，婚事再度撻Q。"},{"pid":"cb506ee4029f90fa015f0705dc61f8db2058fce0","tid":1030463,"uid":43804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f260f8d5fd453a034932f2912114012c373452","tid":1030463,"uid":43804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20190221/s00016/1550688139160/事業得意-愛情觸礁-lady-gaga取消訂婚\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20190221%2Fs00016%2F1550688139160%2F%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%97%E6%84%8F-%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%B8%E7%A4%81-lady-gaga%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%82%E5%A9%9A&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=5304a055\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20190221%2Fs00016%2F1550688139160%2F%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%97%E6%84%8F-%E6%84%9B%E6%83%85%E8%A7%B8%E7%A4%81-lady-gaga%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%82%E5%A9%9A&h=79684533\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20190221/s00016/1550688139160/事業得意-愛情觸礁-lady-gaga取消訂婚</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】百變天后Lady Gaga首次擔正電影《星夢情深》，再次登上事業高峰，不但憑片中歌曲贏得格林美獎項，並首度獲奧斯卡最佳女主角提名，縱橫歌影界，成就非凡；她跟經理人Christian Carino去年宣布訂婚，之後經常在公開場合曬恩愛；可惜一如她在個人紀錄片《Gaga: Five Foot Two》所言，每次事業的成功，她都失去一個重要的人，Gaga前日承認跟Christian解除婚約，並已分手。<br />\n<br />\nLady Gaga本月10日獨自出席格林美音樂頒獎禮，而且訂婚戒指也不見蹤影，眼利的粉絲已質疑Gaga跟未婚夫Christian Carino的感情出現問題；今年情人節，Gaga在社交網也隻字不提未婚夫。<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">日前更盛傳Christian另結新歡，與一名女子到餐廳約會，Gaga迅即承認兩人已解除婚約。</span><br />\n情人節隻字不提未婚夫<br />\n<br />\n事實上，無論是上月的金球獎、影評人選擇大獎，以及演員公會頒獎禮，Lady Gaga跟Christian Carino都是有影皆雙，Gaga在致謝時也會提到對方；但據知情人士透露，兩人分手沒什麽戲劇化過程，只是感情進展得不順利，突然就告吹了。<br />\n<br />\nGaga為串流平台拍攝的紀錄片《Gaga: Five Foot Two》曾提到，<span style=\"color: teal;\">每次她事業上做出點成績，就會失去身邊一個重要的伴侶，就像是一種成交似的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，「當我的唱片銷量超過千萬張，我失去了Matt Williams；當我的唱片銷量達3000萬張，我失去了Luc Carl；當我得到《星夢情深》的演出機會，我失去了泰萊堅尼（Taylor Kinney）」。<br />\n<br />\nGaga跟任職創作總監的Matt Williams於2008年至2010年成為一對，之後跟經營酒吧的Luc Carl拍拖；至於她跟電視劇《芝加哥烈火群英》男星泰萊堅尼的一段關係算最長久，兩人於2011年走在一起，並在2015年的情人節宣布訂婚，但訂婚約一年後宣布分手。<br />\n<br />\nLady Gaga跟經理人Christian的戀情於2017年2月公開，當時Gaga為美式足球超級碗演出綵排，兩人被發現在球場上表現親暱，並於同年11月訂婚，但直到去年10月才公開兩人的未婚夫妻關係，想不到兩人最終未拉埋天窗，已宣布分手。"},{"pid":"fefed2c02aff0a29d87150f04aad991bea33d995","tid":1030463,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fc9279cb4f22062d16e5383da162d6d0862130","tid":1030463,"uid":146435,"like":12,"dislike":36,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢老公知道lady gaga係男人添"},{"pid":"4b8a58a0877335e4af76a01d7686927ea6e9db53","tid":1030463,"uid":43804,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"(show blocked user - METOO者死全家)"},{"pid":"78a5f2f37e7ec00339c19e451aca0231a506a35d","tid":1030463,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102a455e218c7c57f9493ee17c3771067a3c71c6","tid":1030463,"uid":27234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c2ea179e9f240f165ffc79984f64b988fd0483","tid":1030463,"uid":112000,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"希望 Gaga 快啲搵到 Mr. Right <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d79643cad3239d78c